00:47.920 --> 00:49.320
[Man speaking indistinctly
over P.A.]

00:49.360 --> 00:50.680
Receptionist: Good morning.
Family planning.

00:50.720 --> 00:52.040
[Door closes]

00:52.080 --> 00:53.680
Hold.[Telephone ringing]

00:53.720 --> 00:55.320
[Indistinct conversations]

00:55.360 --> 00:56.920
[Ringing continues]

00:56.960 --> 00:59.760
