01:04.560 --> 01:06.400
I'm just pulling up
background on Jaynie Lee

01:06.440 --> 01:07.440
ahead of tomorrow's
meeting.
[Sighs]

01:07.480 --> 01:08.800
[Child coughing]

01:08.840 --> 01:11.440
You know it says
"lifestyle guru,

01:11.480 --> 01:15.000
activist,
syndicated columnist,

01:15.040 --> 01:18.000
and cancer survivor"
on her Wikipedia.

01:18.040 --> 01:21.200
Nowhere does it say she made
her millions from colonic tea.

01:21.240 --> 01:22.520
Ah.

01:22.560 --> 01:24.160
[Indistinct conversation]

01:24.200 --> 01:25.720
♪♪

01:25.760 --> 01:28.800
Well, we all have
our skeletons.

01:28.840 --> 01:30.240
♪♪

01:30.280 --> 01:31.920
-I'm heading in.
-Okay.

01:31.960 --> 01:33.320
[Cellphone beeps]

01:33.360 --> 01:34.960
These?
Mum.

01:35.000 --> 01:38.160
These are not a sign
that you are a grown-up. Okay?

01:38.200 --> 01:39.440
They are not a sign
that you can just

01:39.480 --> 01:41.640
have sex
in the house.

01:41.680 --> 01:43.560
They are so
you don't have a baby.

01:43.600 --> 01:45.200
They're there so I don't
have to bring you back

01:45.240 --> 01:47.320
-to that clinic.
-It's my body.

01:47.360 --> 01:49.240
You don't get to tell me
what to do with my body.

01:49.280 --> 01:50.600
No, I don't.[Brakes squeal]

01:50.640 --> 01:52.600
