perfectly well on your own.

01:52.640 --> 01:54.240
♪♪

01:54.280 --> 01:55.480
I love him.

01:55.520 --> 01:56.640
♪♪

01:56.680 --> 01:59.680
You still need
to use condoms.

01:59.720 --> 02:01.560
They did tell you that?[Seat belt clicks]

02:01.600 --> 02:07.600
♪♪

02:07.640 --> 02:10.320
[Telephone ringing in distance]

02:10.360 --> 02:11.720
Ruth: Nina!

02:11.760 --> 02:13.600
[Ringing continues]

02:14.840 --> 02:17.000
I'm going...
-Insane?

02:17.040 --> 02:18.840
...to Noble & Hale's
summer drinks.

02:18.880 --> 02:19.920
-Tonight?
-Mm.

02:19.960 --> 02:21.120
You never go.

02:21.160 --> 02:23.240
-Yes, I go.
-No, you don't.

02:23.280 --> 02:25.480
Grouped with Christmas parties
and Dress Down Fridays.

02:25.520 --> 02:26.920
Are you trying
to snoop on Hannah?

02:26.960 --> 02:29.080
How else does one check
the competition out?

02:29.120 --> 02:32.120
Keep your friends close
and your enemies closer.

02:32.160 --> 02:34.280
I think
we should be there.

02:36.000 --> 02:37.080
Have you shrunk?

02:38.080 --> 02:39.640
You will, too.

02:39.680 --> 02:41.560
Grandma Dora
came up to here

02:41.600 --> 02:43.200
by the time
she died.

02:43.240 --> 02:45.760
And you are behind
on new business.

02:45.800 --> 02:47.960
A Senior Partner needs
to bring in more --

02:48.000 --> 02:49.880
much more.
Do you want
to scream this out

02:49.920 --> 02:51.320
so everyone can hear

02:51.360 --> 02:53.040
or join me for a cocktail
in the drawing room?

02:55.720 --> 02:57.880
I've asked Donna
to go through our lists.

02:57.920 --> 02:59.360
Do not ask me
to cold-call.

02:59.400 --> 03:00.920
Put in
the occasional call.

03:00.960 --> 03:02.960
Are we pulling
our belts in, Mother?

03:03.000 --> 03:05.840
Simply looking
at ways to build business.

03:05.880 --> 03:08.800
Incidentally, did you
bill for --
250K.

03:08.840 --> 03:11.760
Settled at the 11th hour,
and Donald Kovac called again.

03:11.800 --> 03:13.880
Please say --
Both accounts.

03:13.920 --> 03:15.080
Yes!

03:15.120 --> 03:17.680
[Knock on door]Car's here.

03:17.720 --> 03:19.080
Right,
I'm in court

03:19.120 --> 03:20.800
on the McKenzie case
this afternoon.

03:20.840 --> 03:22.400
I would like you there
as my partner.

03:27.120 --> 03:34.040
♪♪

03:34.080 --> 03:35.880
-Goldie --
-No.

03:35.920 --> 03:37.280
No!

03:37.320 --> 03:38.800
You can screw my husband,

03:38.840 --> 03:41.120
but you are not having
my hairdresser, as well.

03:41.160 --> 03:42.920
I thought you were
in court today.

03:42.960 --> 03:45.360
-I would never have come if --
-Oh, if you'd known I'd be here?

03:45.400 --> 03:46.680
♪♪

03:46.720 --> 03:50.720
I used to tell you
everything--

03:50.760 --> 03:52.520
when I was going out
to do a bit of shopping,

03:52.560 --> 03:55.000
if I was gonna
visit my mum.

03:55.040 --> 03:57.080
Must have made it
much easier for you.

03:57.120 --> 03:58.400
-Please.
-No, no, I'm --

03:58.440 --> 03:59.960
I'm glad he had company.

04:00.000 --> 04:01.200
Must have been
hard for him,

04:01.240 --> 04:03.640
living with
an alcoholic like me.

04:03.680 --> 04:04.760
♪♪

04:04.800 --> 04:06.640
But give it
a few years.

04:06.680 --> 04:10.080
It'll become the "last job
of the day" for you, too.

04:10.120 --> 04:16.320
♪♪

04:16.360 --> 04:19.760
[Voice breaking]
It's his birthday on Friday.

04:19.800 --> 04:22.280
Hi, Danny!

04:22.320 --> 04:24.640
Well, I am
his Godmother.

04:26.880 --> 04:28.560
You saying I'd forget?

04:30.840 --> 04:32.000
[Footsteps]

04:32.040 --> 04:33.440
[Door opens, bell chimes]

04:34.800 --> 04:36.840
[Cellphone ringing]

04:40.680 --> 04:42.400
[Knock on door, door opens]

04:42.440 --> 04:44.800
Your sister
keeps calling.

04:44.840 --> 04:45.840
Yes.

04:45.880 --> 04:47.600
[Ringing stops]

04:47.640 --> 04:48.640
The McKenzie FDA.[Door closes]

04:48.680 --> 04:50.640
This afternoon.

04:50.680 --> 04:52.800
Copy of Davey's accounts
that Goldie found.

04:52.840 --> 04:53.880
Thank you.

05:00.760 --> 05:02.720
[Door closes]

05:05.560 --> 05:14.120
