05:30.480 --> 05:31.640
♪♪

05:31.680 --> 05:33.080
Thanks for those
bank statements.

05:33.120 --> 05:35.040
By the way...

05:35.080 --> 05:37.040
good hair.

05:37.080 --> 05:38.880
Big day.

05:38.920 --> 05:41.000
Mother wants you
by her side.
Pick up
your sodding phone.

05:41.040 --> 05:42.760
We need to talk.

05:42.800 --> 05:45.640
♪♪

05:45.680 --> 05:47.160
Nina:
Excuse me.

05:47.200 --> 05:49.760
♪♪

05:49.800 --> 05:51.400
Oh, thank you.

05:51.440 --> 05:53.080
♪♪

05:53.120 --> 05:54.880
Thanks.Nina, no.

05:54.920 --> 05:56.360
[Clears throat]

05:56.400 --> 05:59.520
♪♪

05:59.560 --> 06:01.760
