get to speak?You don't.

06:01.800 --> 06:04.200
That's what
your barrister's for.

06:04.240 --> 06:06.680
Bailiff: All rise.

06:06.720 --> 06:08.200
[Footsteps]

06:08.240 --> 06:13.120
♪♪

06:13.160 --> 06:19.480
♪♪

06:19.520 --> 06:21.080
[Thumps]

06:21.120 --> 06:23.920
It's impossible for us
to have an effective FDA today

06:23.960 --> 06:25.440
because the husband
has not given

06:25.480 --> 06:28.840
a sufficient disclosure
regarding his assets.

06:28.880 --> 06:31.080
We would like
Mr. McKenzie to confirm

06:31.120 --> 06:33.440
that the Form E
accurately reflects

06:33.480 --> 06:36.400
and discloses
all subsidiary accounts.

06:36.440 --> 06:38.960
