an unacceptable request.

06:39.000 --> 06:40.280
My apologies
to the applicant

06:40.320 --> 06:41.680
that it wasn't included
in the bundle,

06:41.720 --> 06:43.480
but it has only just
come to light.

06:43.520 --> 06:45.840
Permission to present
a document to Your Honor?

06:48.720 --> 06:50.720
As you will see,
we have concerns

06:50.760 --> 06:52.440
with regard
to an unnamed account

06:52.480 --> 06:54.680
to which a number
of sizable deposits

06:54.720 --> 06:56.760
have been made
over the last three years,

06:56.800 --> 06:59.040
possibly longer.

06:59.080 --> 07:01.440
We'd like full disclosure
of this account...
[Sighs]
Why were these not...

07:01.480 --> 07:02.480
...and any other
omissions.

07:02.520 --> 07:03.560
Why were these not --

07:03.600 --> 07:04.760
-You broke in?
-Shh.

07:04.800 --> 07:06.640
-You broke into my office!
-Shh!

07:06.680 --> 07:08.560
Which she was able
to legally access

07:08.600 --> 07:11.040
within her capacity
as Company Secretary.

07:11.080 --> 07:13.080
Judge Aspen: Ms. Grace.

07:13.120 --> 07:14.840
I'm disappointed
by this omission.

07:14.880 --> 07:17.920
The proper process
is expected in my court.

07:17.960 --> 07:19.560
We cannot proceed.

07:19.600 --> 07:21.720
-This is a farce!
-Be quiet.

07:21.760 --> 07:24.240
Or I'll have you
thrown out.

07:24.280 --> 07:27.640
Stanley:
We request that a Penal Notice
is attached to the Judge's order

07:27.680 --> 07:30.160
so that we can apply
to commit Mr. McKenzie to prison

07:30.200 --> 07:31.400
if he breaches it again.

07:31.440 --> 07:32.560
Judge Aspen: Agreed.

07:32.600 --> 07:33.560
[Scoffs]

07:33.600 --> 07:34.840
[Chair scrapes]

07:34.880 --> 07:37.040
-I want you out of the house.
-Shh!

07:37.080 --> 07:39.080
When we next meet,

07:39.120 --> 07:40.960
a new Form E
will have been submitted

07:41.000 --> 07:42.920
with all
the relevant accounts.

07:42.960 --> 07:46.680
♪♪

07:46.720 --> 07:49.880
[Wheels scraping]

07:49.920 --> 07:53.240
[Wheels scraping lightly]

07:53.280 --> 07:56.560
-Book club on Thursday.
-Yes! Lovely.

07:56.600 --> 07:57.720
[Chuckles]

08:01.520 --> 08:03.720
You just won that round
for them, Mr. McKenzie.

08:03.760 --> 08:05.120
Then you should
have let me speak.

08:05.160 --> 08:07.440
I've been running meetings
since I was 19.

08:07.480 --> 08:09.920
I had my first board
by the time I was 23.

08:10.760 --> 08:13.120
You. You --
I'm coming for you.

08:13.160 --> 08:15.120
Advise your client
to resist making threats,

08:15.160 --> 08:17.160
or he'll be facing
more than contempt of court.

08:17.200 --> 08:19.320
She was meant to settle.
You said she'd settle.

08:19.360 --> 08:22.640
No, I said possibly
she would settle.

08:22.680 --> 08:24.280
I also warned you that,

08:24.320 --> 08:25.720
if she listened
to her solicitor,

08:25.760 --> 08:27.400
she may
very well proceed,

08:27.440 --> 08:29.840
particularly if they found
anything incriminating,

08:29.880 --> 08:31.280
like certain
bank statements

08:31.320 --> 08:33.720
about which you may
have failed to tell me.

08:33.760 --> 08:35.600
Now, clearly, they did.

08:37.200 --> 08:39.520
[Quietly] If you
have been moving funds,

08:39.560 --> 08:43.560
I would rather not have this
conversation in a public place.

08:43.600 --> 08:45.080
Now, it's a stressful time.

08:45.120 --> 08:47.360
Perhaps you forgot
that you had done so.

08:47.400 --> 08:50.040
It happens.
This is your first divorce.

08:50.080 --> 08:52.720
It most certainly
is not mine.

08:52.760 --> 08:55.360
If you want me
to help you, from now on,

08:55.400 --> 08:57.000
I will need to know

08:57.040 --> 09:00.080
exactly how much
you forgot.

09:00.120 --> 09:01.520
Now, until then,

09:01.560 --> 09:03.800
send over everything you have
to Noble & Hale.

09:03.840 --> 09:05.920
Bury them in bank statements,

09:05.960 --> 09:07.880
tax receipts,
back-dated VAT claims --

09:07.920 --> 09:09.880
every shred
you can find --

09:09.920 --> 09:11.240
and then pray that,

09:11.280 --> 09:13.880
between now
and our next court date,

09:13.920 --> 09:15.160
it will not be enough time

09:15.200 --> 09:17.400
for them to actually
go through everything.

09:17.440 --> 09:20.640
Now, calm
as you walk out.

09:24.120 --> 09:25.880
[Indistinct conversations]

09:25.920 --> 09:27.880
I really never read
that to you?

09:27.920 --> 09:29.320
[Conversations continue]

09:29.360 --> 09:30.360
Uh...

09:32.000 --> 09:34.480
Oh. Must have been,
uh...

09:34.520 --> 09:36.720
Hannah and Nina, then.Yeah.

09:36.760 --> 09:40.920
[Conversations continue]

09:40.960 --> 09:44.200
♪♪

09:44.240 --> 09:46.800
[Chuckles]

09:46.840 --> 09:48.360
Cool drawings.

09:48.400 --> 09:50.880
It's a bit young
for Vinnie and Tills.

09:50.920 --> 09:52.520
[Book thumps lightly]

09:52.560 --> 09:53.880
[Glass taps]

09:53.920 --> 09:57.360
That is, um --
That is a beautiful ring.

09:57.400 --> 09:59.640
Oh, it's --
Oh, it was
my grandmother's.

09:59.680 --> 10:02.120
-Oh.
-It's the original setting.

10:02.160 --> 10:04.160
-It's -- It's very --
-Big.

10:04.200 --> 10:06.600
[Chuckles]

10:06.640 --> 10:08.200
Yeah, I need to...

10:08.240 --> 10:11.360
[Conversations continue]

10:11.400 --> 10:14.240
...um, get it --
Sorry, just...

10:14.280 --> 10:15.760
[Footsteps]

10:15.800 --> 10:18.440
[Conversations continue]

10:18.480 --> 10:20.480
It's the wedding.

10:20.520 --> 10:22.800
It's just overwhelming.

10:22.840 --> 10:24.480
You start
with the idea of it,

10:24.520 --> 10:26.000
and then shabang.

10:26.040 --> 10:28.560
[Breathes sharply]

10:28.600 --> 10:30.040
Nerf Guns.

10:30.080 --> 10:31.320
[Conversations continue]

10:31.360 --> 10:34.440
Now, that is some
bad grandpa shit.

10:34.480 --> 10:36.320
[Chuckling] Oh!

10:36.360 --> 10:38.400
[Chuckles]
Uh. Uh, yes.

10:38.440 --> 10:42.040
[Conversations continue]

10:42.080 --> 10:46.120
♪♪

10:46.160 --> 10:49.520
-A lot to take in.
-Mm.

10:49.560 --> 10:52.080
I wasn't here,
and now I am here.

10:52.120 --> 10:54.520
It's not that
I'm not pleased.

10:54.560 --> 10:56.640
[Conversations continue]

11:00.520 --> 11:04.640
"Happiness is a large,

11:04.680 --> 11:07.440
loving,
close-knit family

11:07.480 --> 11:09.320
