11:10.840 --> 11:14.240
My father had that
above his desk.

11:14.280 --> 11:16.080
A miserable bastard.

11:16.120 --> 11:18.600
Terminal dinners
when I was a child,

11:18.640 --> 11:20.960
sitting alone
with my mother.

11:21.000 --> 11:24.680
I used to imagine that he had
a family somewhere else.

11:24.720 --> 11:27.640
I swore I would never do that
with my own kids.

11:27.680 --> 11:30.160
♪♪

11:30.200 --> 11:32.920
I wondered if you would like
your father

11:32.960 --> 11:34.640
to walk you
down the aisle.

11:34.680 --> 11:40.720
♪♪

11:40.760 --> 11:43.320
[Indistinct conversations]

11:43.360 --> 11:46.840
[Footsteps]

11:46.880 --> 11:48.680
Uh, he just --

11:48.720 --> 11:50.640
he wants to walk me
down the aisle.

11:53.720 --> 11:55.600
-Wow, incredible.
-Thank you.

11:55.640 --> 11:58.720
♪♪

11:58.760 --> 12:02.080
-Um, don't you have work?
-Yes. Yeah. Um...

12:02.120 --> 12:03.320
Can we give you
a lift?

12:03.360 --> 12:05.560
Uh, no, I'll --
I'll -- I'll walk.

12:05.600 --> 12:07.560
Bye.

12:07.600 --> 12:09.520
James. James.
Oh.

12:09.560 --> 12:11.920
[Laughs]

12:11.960 --> 12:14.080
[Chuckles]

12:14.120 --> 12:15.640
♪♪

12:15.680 --> 12:17.600
[Footsteps]

12:17.640 --> 12:24.000
♪♪

12:24.040 --> 12:25.320
